* Add PBR files to .gitignore
* Enable coverage testing
* Discover package for py2.6 tests
* Fixup and start travis build
* Convert tests to testr, add flake8 tox command
* More reorganizing
* Rework ideas
* Added a simple README file
* Initial commit
